name: Onna-Bugeisha Series Jade
description:
Onna-Bugeisha is a woman who is skilled in martial arts and is good at using weapons such as katana, arrows, and spears.
She sometimes wears a suit of armor or just wears a kimono.
She always wears a mask, and in this series, she wears a jade mask.
